        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl mb-6">
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Base64 Encoding</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-8">
            Encode and decode data using Base64 format. Useful for binary data in text-based contexts like JSON, URLs, and HTTP headers.
        </p>
