                        <code class="text-lg font-mono text-indigo-400">Embedding Binary in JSON</code>
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 text-gray-500 transition-opacity" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">Encode binary data like images or files to include in JSON payloads.</p>
<pre data-filename="Example"><code class="language-soli text-sm">let image_data = slurp("avatar.png")
let base64_image = Base64.encode(image_data)
let json_response = json_stringify({
    "avatar": base64_image,
    "filename": "avatar.png"
});</code></pre>
